#
#   This entry is the Rust=183 leader bump that **OPENS** Axis 128
#   (pure-Rust IETF QUIC 1 transport protocol / quinn ecosystem)
#   at 1/0/0 following R1081 _gondolin (TS-Node=182 CLOSED Axis
#   127 pure-Rust+Go+JS SSH 2.0 at 1/1/1 with triple-182 landmark
#   + 120th axis closed).  R1083 on deck: Go=183 continues Axis
#   128 via a Go consumer of `quic-go/quic-go` — Marten Seemann's
#   canonical pure-Go QUIC 1 implementation, the dominant Go-side
#   QUIC library behind every modern Go HTTP/3 client/server
